task.summary:
SetChunkSize messages now properly sent to connecting clients.
Previously SetChunkSize messages failed because we only sent the message that our max was X bytes, but we never updated ChunkIo to make sure it would serialize up to X bytes in a single chunk. This has been fixed and now we are writing chunks of the proper sizes.
Audio and Video messages now pass their original timestamps through.
